If you are a Photoshopper this is definitely a torrent for you.

I've been working with the plug-ins now and almost everyone works great. There was a few plug-ins that were missing a crack or serial / license.

Digital Anarchy Prismatte 3.0 - Missing crack/Invalid license.
Imagininomic - Missing crack/Invalid license.

The Digital Film Tool series requires some extra attention to crack, but it's not really a big problem. Install plug-in> copy the crack into the install dir> launch PS CS3.

As I said earlier every plug-in is compatible with PhotoShop CS3.
